graph TD
    A["User Message<br/>(e.g., My son Des is 12<br/>Actually he's 14)"] -->|Step 1| B["Check for Corrections<br/>(Look for: actually, wrong,<br/>corrected to, meant to say)"]

    B -->|Found| C["LLM Extracts Correction<br/>(What changed?)<br/>Old: age=12<br/>New: age=14<br/>Who: Des"]

    C --> D["Flag as User Correction<br/>(Will skip validation staging,<br/>goes straight to database)"]

    B -->|Not Found| E["Check for Retractions<br/>(Look for: forget, delete,<br/>no longer true, not true)"]

    E -->|Found| F["LLM Extracts Retraction<br/>(What's being removed?)<br/>Subject: Des<br/>Fact: age<br/>Action: delete or archive)"]

    F --> G["Flag as Retraction<br/>(Skip normal storage,<br/>route to removal path)"]

    E -->|Not Found| H["Normal Extraction<br/>(Extract new facts<br/>from conversation)"]

    H --> I["LLM Identifies Fact Elements<br/>Entity: Des (type: Person)<br/>Relationship: age<br/>Value: 12 (type: Number)<br/>Confidence: 95%"]

    I --> J{Is This Relationship<br/>Already Defined?}

    J -->|Yes, in Database| K["Load Relationship Rules<br/>(Is it bidirectional?<br/>Does it have constraints?)<br/>Use established pattern"]

    J -->|No, New Pattern| L["Mark as New Pattern<br/>(Will be evaluated later)<br/>Store with low confidence<br/>until approved)"]

    K --> M["Validate Against Rules<br/>(Does entity type fit?<br/>Does value type fit?<br/>Is direction correct?)"]

    L --> M

    M -->|Failed| N["Lower Confidence Score<br/>(Flag as uncertain,<br/>may need manual review)"]

    M -->|Passed| O["Fact Ready to Store<br/>(All elements validated<br/>ready for database)"]

    N --> O

    O --> P["Send to Storage Pipeline<br/>(Include: correction flag,<br/>retraction flag, validation<br/>results, confidence score)"]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style D fill:#fff9c4
    style G fill:#ffcdd2
    style L fill:#f3e5f5
    style O fill:#c8e6c9
